4. DERIVATIVE WORKS
   Derivative works must maintain the charitable distribution mechanism
   and remain subject to this license. Removing or modifying the charitable
   distribution mechanism constitutes a material breach.

5. NO CIRCUMVENTION
   You may NOT:
   - Remove, disable, or modify the charitable distribution mechanism
   - Reduce the charitable percentage below 7%
   - Delay or prevent charitable distributions
   - Use the Software in ways that undermine its charitable mission

6. AUTOMATIC TERMINATION
   This license terminates automatically if you violate any term, particularly
